elements.title: a house in Ohio

elements.title: hive cities
elements.contents: ... that urbanists have used hive cities from the science-fiction universe of Warhammer 40,000 as an example of how vertical cities could become dystopian?

elements.title: Philippine embassy in Pretoria
elements.contents: ... that the Philippine embassy in Pretoria responded to a South African newspaper's denunciation of horse fighting in the Philippines by saying that the practice was already illegal?

elements.title: Jules Rabin
elements.contents: ... that artisan baker Jules Rabin was inspired to bake bread after a 1971 visit to a commune in France where "they didn't speak of bread as holy, but they treated it as a holy object"?

elements.title: Tout est lumière
elements.contents: ... that Tout est lumière, a setting by Maurice Ravel for soprano, choir and orchestra of a poem by Victor Hugo, earned Ravel a place in the second round of the 1901 Prix de Rome?

elements.title: Battle of Nanggulon
